==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Mollebart
<hw>Mol"le*bart</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>An agricultural
implement used in Flanders, consisting of a kind of large shovel drawn
by a horse and guided by a man.</def> <altsp>[Written also
<asp>mollebaert</asp> and <asp>mouldebaert</asp>.]</altsp>
<rj><au>Simmonds.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Mollemoke</ent>⟦br⟧
